metadata.name: CosmoMask #1
metadata.description:
**CosmoMask #1**

 By owning a [CosmoMask NFT](https://thecosmomasks.com/?utm_source=OpenSea&utm_medium=mask_description), you accumulate a [CosmoMasks Power (CMP)](https://info.uniswap.org/token/0xB9FDc13F7f747bAEdCc356e9Da13Ab883fFa719B) every day. That allows you to choose a name for your NFT on the Ethereum Blockchain and earn [COSMO](https://info.uniswap.org/token/0x27cd7375478F189bdcF55616b088BE03d9c4339c) on the [CosmoSwap.space](https://cosmoswap.space/farms?utm_source=OpenSea&utm_medium=mask_description).

 Be the first owner of a CosmoMask and get a bonus of 10,000 [COSMO](https://info.uniswap.org/token/0x27cd7375478F189bdcF55616b088BE03d9c4339c) and 1,830 [CMP](https://info.uniswap.org/token/0xB9FDc13F7f747bAEdCc356e9Da13Ab883fFa719B) for each mask!
